Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}ha Epephlegon Sodoma,Hamartolous,Eis Choun Thanatou{\r}\N火與硫磺  讓有罪之人  變成死灰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Jovis Tempestas Fulguriens{\r}\N雷之暴風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Ourania Phlogosis{\r}\N燃燒的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了  涅吉小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.54,0:01:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  總有一天還會見面！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}學園祭結束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是…古奈爾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以今天會來找你  是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  他現在還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「英國」指的就是回威爾士之事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有通往魔法世界的大門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定回威爾士…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許…這一去就不回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}然後  放暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不允許你就這麼一去不回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我保證你一定會回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你身為我們班主任的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個社團就是大家為了和你一起找到父親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且確保你能平安回到學園而成立的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名譽顧問？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初我是沒有回絕過你們啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當真想把我的別墅當作活動室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧  大家加油修行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}大家的修行開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  真的倒下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  這樣一來我也會超能力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太完美了  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！  既然如此  我們一決勝負吧  古菲！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！  隨時奉陪！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Imperium Graphices Inferno Aniki{\r}\N落書帝國  炎之魔人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎形拳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刹  快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小刹你受傷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我的道具只能治療3分鐘以內的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真沒用  對不起啦  小刹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許舔一下就能治好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐…你居然…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  已經完成78小時的學習了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆真不簡單…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  接下來就由我來教授你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼…拿走！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續7天  我已經堅持下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有什麼話說？
