Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往後在國內外的情報收集活動中都能獲得強大的多方支援
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下滿意了吧  小鬼們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然很滿意  那還不快回個話！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你縮水啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本體正在翻修…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真好真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒哦
