Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的三人組
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服好普通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不搭調
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為同伴  為什麼不再裝扮得更奇幻一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去！  男子校服可是我的戰鬥服！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我作為顧問而…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啥時候成為她們的伙伴啦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  千雨不是我們的同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…現有成員還真是壯觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡  好戲還在後頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:08:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的道具也是越磨練越博大精深
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  修行萬歲！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家還想不斷提升能力呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是群悠閒的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到這幫人是我的伙伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的頭疼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  伙伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  慢著  才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啥時候成為她們的伙伴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小傢伙們都高興得不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣  大家能如此積極讓我非常欣慰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候出發？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預訂為8月12日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有兩個多禮拜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過充其量也就是在首都轉轉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再遠的話…也只能去逛逛附近的觀光地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒指望光靠這個暑假就能查明父親的行蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過嘛  你們就當作觀光去領略一下魔法國度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～  大家想去英國嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都想去！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快完成修行  向威爾士進發！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:11.55,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}「要前往何處呢？吉爾…」…出自結婚塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:11.55,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}「期待第四（回）？！」這次OAD預計只有三集…貼這紙條的意思又是要看DVD銷量嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到囉  聽到囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大新聞到手！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唰～  撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓姐親傳  隱秘逃脫術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了  明日菜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是調查結果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦  我沒等多久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效率挺高的嘛  班長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪廣財團一出手  這種程度的調查簡直易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且  這不是因為你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…而是為了涅吉老師而做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  到底怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…看來涅吉老師的父親納吉·斯普林菲爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:59.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除雪廣綾香外禁止閱覽  關於納吉·斯普林菲爾德的第一次調查報告書\N雪廣財團國際情報部門  綜合情報分析部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確在10年前就已經下落不明了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他並沒有去世呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚  總之目前下落不明…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界下落不明…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  最終還是在魔法世界裡囉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:13.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是能找到的最全的文本資料了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要繼續深入調查…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…需要花費大量人員和時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  如果為了涅吉老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界萬人規模的調查我也在所不辭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  慢著慢著  不用做到那一步啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經有線索了  暫時就免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝啦  班長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你  我們離涅吉的父親又近了許多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜你這叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…什麼意思嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟什麼事  蒔繪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長你給我評評理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:59.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}請稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了尋找涅吉老師的父親而組建了新社團
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞞著我們卿卿我我遠赴英國舉辦合宿旅行！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有…我們並沒有故意瞞著你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更談不上卿卿我我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好你個明日菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一方面騙我給你提供情報…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這種重大活動反而要瞞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書店妹妹和春春也會一起去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然將我們排除在外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜你這壞女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  新社團會舉辦合宿旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但儘管去的是英國  同時還得去些特殊的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為此我們從學園祭開始就一直特訓到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊？  要去山上嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是啊是啊  有攀岩什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能帶沒有接受過訓練的人去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種爛理由誰信啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:11:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…班長？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還我  還我  還我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  好慢！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好快！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒔繪同學  鳴瀧姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住那個壞女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招  明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶  抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住她！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  班長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後一定會向你道謝的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學  什麼時候這麼厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼狽不狼狽啊  班長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依…依文潔琳同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依文
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新社團…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名譽顧問！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也給你們一個試試本領的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我們是同學嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們在鬧些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天正好是夏日祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能去英國旅行的新社團！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓  裕奈你小聲點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼有趣的活動膽敢瞞著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果通過了依文給出的入團測驗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該也能去英國吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些新社團的成員待會貌似會去參加夏日祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新社團的全體成員都會佩戴這種別針徽章
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰搶到它  我就追加批准她入部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納吉先生說不定會出現在涅吉的故鄉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…裕奈  不是這麼回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看準時機奪取徽章  聽起來並不難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛  也不是那麼簡單的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:09.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英國文化研究社團  涅吉魔社（暫定）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些成員是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長瀨同學  櫻咲同學  古菲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻帆良武道會的猛將們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們身上似乎完全沒有可乘之機…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且明日菜也很強…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月不穿浴衣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要回店裡一趟…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是古菲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說曹操…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那誰就到啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確戴著白色徽章呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對手可是小古啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書館的兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  這個徽章究竟是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  社團成員的標誌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是咱們的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是  對最溫和的兩位下手會不會太卑鄙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:15:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻其弱點乃兵法之本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了確保英國之旅…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這也是沒辦法的辦法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩具槍從哪來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小家敗氣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該稱讚我行事謹慎才對！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和學園祭的氛圍又有所不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是撈金魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要來比一比
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到還能跟小刹一起參加祭典呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩位關係也很親密呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶茶丸同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徽章？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在分發給部裡的每一個成員…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是主人送給各位的特別禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～這是什麼？  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以收下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個徽章就是社團成員的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家能佩戴好出席今晚的祭典…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴  我一定戴  太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼要做成白色翅膀形狀的徽章呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依文居然送我們禮物…真可疑…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人不願意社團一直被稱為「涅吉魔社（暫定）」才…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…總之主人就是不樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幹！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總體來說主人是模仿了Thousand Master的赤色羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而將它稱為白色羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…羽翼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好啊  這名稱不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…怎麼行…我總覺得呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依文也挺懂得風雅的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對她刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那個徽章是社團成員的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以去英國之前弄丟了徽章的人將被強行勸退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:16:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:17:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要奪走那個徽章  就能去英國旅行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人好像也進行過那啥特殊訓練吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  先看我表現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  那邊的兩位小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的徽章很不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是剛好路過的徽章迷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徽章仙士  徽章人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很中意你們那徽章…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想受傷的話就把東西交出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊  裕奈同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼露餡了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是夕映吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～  不算  剛剛那個不算哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你們就當作什麼也發生過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢！  兩位的徽章都很可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.87,0:17:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼徽章來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能借我們看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個是剛剛依文潔琳同學給的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這徽章真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能借來看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  這可不能隨便借…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥？  借一下而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是拿在手上看一下而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…你們為什麼突然對這種普普通通的徽章…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不普通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚  好想拿在手裡看一看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看…就是這個白白的有點像翅膀的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好銷魂啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒔繪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～為什麼啊  小夕映
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼嘛  夕映吉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼為什麼啊  真是太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們另有企圖吧  裕奈同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管了！  逮住她們！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你們搞什麼名堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位真不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Practe Biginar
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Lux{\r}\N光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快逃  和香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  既然你們不賞臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向敵人開炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Elementa Aerialia,Venti Apirantes{\r}\N大地的精靈  瞬息之風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Cito Aeuntes Ac Inimicis Meis Me Defendant{\r}\N降臨至此  保護吾等禦於外敵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Limes Aerialis{\r}\N風陣結界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧！  居然彈開了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Practe Biginar
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Vente{\r}\N風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕映好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這難道就是特訓成果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  大家分頭追
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕映好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的跟魔法師一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  對裕奈同學她們用魔法真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們的行動很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛拿到徽章立刻就發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是依文潔琳同學對部內成員進行的考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能是一種考試
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果徽章被奪走…我們就會失去部內成員的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個想法應該沒錯吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可不能被她們抓住  和香  用你的道具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Diaria Ejus{\r}\N本我繪圖日記
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Minora Quadrupla{\r}\N簡易小型版4分冊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Adeant{\r}\N顯現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Tumcogitationes Vestigent De{\r}\N追蹤思考
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Sasacie Macie{\r}\N佐佐木蒔繪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Acasie Juna{\r}\N明石裕奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Oocoutie Acira{\r}\N大和內晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}et Izumie Acone{\r}\N和泉亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:50.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}7月27日  裕奈    嗚～  太大意了  實在是出乎意料  但…但是還不能放棄！  就算是為了亞子也要拿到手  首先是兵分兩路  西邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  就可以實時追蹤四個人的思維了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是和香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓我們來完美地逃脫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典很好玩呢  楓姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  確實不假呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自爆了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那裡的小姐們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徽章蠻不錯的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖把東西給交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去重練過再來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起  小姐們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲部長實在太強大了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  那個肌肉大叔是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.68,0:21:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春春的男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕映跟和香  哪裡都找不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  兩個小鬼有兩下子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊班長  我們失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.65,0:21:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啦  不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我親自出馬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一決勝負！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班…班長你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.01,0:22:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學…以前還基本跟我打平手的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候拉開了那麼大的距離…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班…班長？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不能在這裡放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要認真出手了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.68,0:22:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.94,0:22:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪廣綾香流  合氣柔術
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天地分斷掌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.72,0:22:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺如何啊  明日菜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長拼盡全力也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:22:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:22:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學和班長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來一直當明日菜是武藝方面的勁敵…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.49,0:23:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情…太恥辱了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.51,0:23:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我…有經過特訓所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有破綻！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.32,0:23:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…搞什麼啊  班長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了  太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.85,0:23:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學  笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.27,0:23:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子脾氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.49,0:23:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  快把那個徽章交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.10,0:23:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了那個徽章  就能加入社團了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.16,0:23:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.17,0:23:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…原來如此啊  依文
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦惱吧  苦惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.54,0:23:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起啊  班長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.88,0:23:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個徽章實在…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.87,0:23:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光你們去太不公平了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.85,0:23:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:23:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是  那邊搞不好會很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.40,0:23:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.43,0:24:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會危險？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要特訓才能應對的危險究竟是指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.80,0:24:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓涅吉老師到那種地方去！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.95,0:24:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然你們也不准去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作為班長…不批准
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.52,0:24:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真那麼危險的話  去找警察之類的正規機構不是更好…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.53,0:24:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能這麼簡單倒好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.14,0:24:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了  告訴你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.75,0:24:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞞著你們真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.92,0:24:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.42,0:24:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果涅吉他不靠自己找到父親的行蹤  就沒有任何意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.80,0:24:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親的事情他要不做個了結的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.98,0:24:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就一步也邁不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.30,0:24:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也終於明白  他是那麼一個麻煩的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.79,0:24:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們才決定幫他一把
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.77,0:24:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.57,0:24:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.35,0:24:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.42,0:25:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.80,0:25:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.77,0:25:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊…沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.86,0:25:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦  涅吉老師
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.40,0:25:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  涅吉弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.77,0:25:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去不去吃炒麵？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.11,0:25:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒麵嗎？  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.11,0:25:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學  我明白你們的決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.97,0:25:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  班長你明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.14,0:25:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.33,0:25:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼重要的事情一直瞞著我  實在是不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.35,0:25:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭要給我好好解釋清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.11,0:25:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕～
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.81,0:25:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.83,0:25:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙  喊著來接人家現在卻沒半個人影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.28,0:25:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.82,0:26:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}涅吉魔社（暫定）正在增值
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.34,0:26:21.21,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}ずっと隠していた
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.46,0:26:28.19,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}君の弱さ　強がるふり
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.09,0:26:35.13,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}どんな辛い日々も
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.41,0:26:41.57,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}顔を上げて　微笑むの
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.66,0:26:49.21,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}子供の頃に見た夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.79,0:26:59.24,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}胸打つ鼓動　扉の外待ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.65,0:27:03.89,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}舞い降りてきた　白い天使よ
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.09,0:27:07.33,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}次の風を味方につけて
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.54,0:27:10.84,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}前よりずっと　輝いてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.03,0:27:17.39,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1000)}大地を蹴り　高く遠くへ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.34,0:26:21.21,ed中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}總是隱藏起這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.46,0:26:28.19,ed中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}把你所有弱點　逞強的掩飾著
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.09,0:26:35.13,ed中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}在那辛酸的時日中
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.41,0:26:41.57,ed中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}也總要仰起臉　透露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.66,0:26:49.21,ed中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}小時候曾經感到美好的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.79,0:26:59.24,ed中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}胸中不斷的跳動　在夢境的門口一直等待
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.65,0:27:03.89,ed中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}飛舞著降臨下的白色的天使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.09,0:27:07.33,ed中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}下次讓風也來　而成為我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.54,0:27:10.84,ed中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}比先前更加明亮　一直都發光閃耀
